[TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167), [IntegrityFlag](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#36-74), [SignalSummary](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#76-94), [AudienceSummaries](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#96-117), [AuditLogEntry](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#169-195), [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210), [AnomalyQueueItem](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#233-241), [OverrideRequest](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#219-231), [WeightedSignal](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/internal.py#91-112)

**Derived types we must create (frontend only):**
`TrustTier` (union), `ConfidenceLevel` (union), `FlagSeverity` (union), `RequestorRole` (union), `LicensingDecision` (union), `TierHistoryPoint`, `AuditEntry`, `AgencyInfo`, `MetricCardData`

