### 1.6 Potential Conflicts

- **`data_is_stale`**: exists on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210) but NOT on [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167). Fixtures must include it.
- **`explanation`**: exists on [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167) but NOT on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210). Admin panel uses full [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167) internally; response only has `summary`.
- **`signal_summary`**: exists on [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167), not on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210). Fixtures must include it for metric cards.

