## Section 5: Data Flow Diagram

### Seeker
```
Page load → useAgencyList() → FIXTURES=true ? getFixture() : fetch(/trust-profile) 
         → builds agencyProfiles[] → MetricCard receives counts
         → TrustTierDistributionBar receives tier distribution
         → AgencyTable receives sorted profile rows
         → Row click → selectedAgencyId state → SeekerAgencyPanel receives profile
```

### Consultant
```
Page load → useTrustProfile(myAgencyId, 'hr_consultant')
         → FIXTURES=true ? getFixture(id) : fetch(/trust-profile/:id)
         → MetricCard receives signal_summary fields
         → useTierHistory(myAgencyId) → TierHistoryChart receives history[]
         → BenchmarkBar receives (agencyValue, platformAvg) tuples
         → ConsultantProfilePanel receives audience_summaries.hr_consultant
```

### Admin
```
Page load → useAgencyList() → all profiles
         → useAnomalyQueue() → AnomalyQueueRow[] rendered
         → MetricCard receives platform-wide computed values
         → PlatformHealthChart receives tier-per-day mock data
         → AgencyTable receives all profiles
         → Row click → selectedAgencyId → useTrustProfile(id, 'admin')
         → useAuditTrail(id) → AdminAgencyPanel receives full data
```

### Licensing
```
Page load → useAgencyList() → all profiles
         → computeLicensingDecision() maps each → PASS / REVIEW / FAIL
         → MetricCard receives decision counts
         → AgencyTable receives sorted by decision (FAIL first)
         → Row click → LicensingDecisionPanel receives profile + decision
```

