## Section 7: Risk Register

| # | Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|---|---|---|
| R1 | `data_is_stale` exists on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210) but not on [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167). | Fixtures may miss it. | Add `data_is_stale: boolean` to fixture TrustProfile type. |
| R2 | No `explanation` on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210) — only `summary`. | Admin panel needs `explanation` — full profile. | Fixtures store full [TrustProfile](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#119-167) with `explanation`. Admin hook returns full profile. |
| R3 | `signal_summary` not on [TrustProfileResponse](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#197-210). | Metric cards need raw signal data. | Fixtures include `signal_summary`. Hooks serve full profile from fixtures. |
| R4 | Platform averages (22%, 3.8, 3.5) are from the PRD but not in [constants.py](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/config/constants.py) as exported values. | Hardcoded in frontend. | Define `PLATFORM_AVERAGES` constant in [types/index.ts](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia-dashboard/src/types/index.ts). |
| R5 | `PlatformHealthChart` needs 30 days of tier-per-day data, but fixtures only have 12 history points per agency. | Chart data gap. | Generate synthetic 30-day platform data in fixtures. |
| R6 | `agency_tenure_days` is on [SignalSummary](file:///d:/JSO%20assignment/atia/models/outputs.py#76-94) but no `registered_at` field in fixtures. | "New This Month" metric card needs registration date. | Add `registered_at` to `AgencyInfo` type and fixtures. |
| R7 | React Query not currently in dependencies. | Hooks won't compile. | Install `@tanstack/react-query` in Step 0. |

